<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbd8e1765-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s6298"><num value="6298">§ 6298.</num><heading> Rules</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission and the Secretary may each issue such rules as each deems necessary to carry out the provisions of this part.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbd8e1766-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/94/163/tIII/s328">Pub. L. 94–163, title III, § 328</ref>, <date date="1975-12-22">Dec. 22, 1975</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/89/928">89 Stat. 928</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/95/619/tVI/s691/b/2">Pub. L. 95–619, title VI, § 691(b)(2)</ref>, <date date="1978-11-09">Nov. 9, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3288">92 Stat. 3288</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbd8e1767-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbd8e1768-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbd8e1769-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1978—<ref href="/us/pl/95/619">Pub. L. 95–619</ref> substituted “Secretary” for “Administrator”, meaning Administrator of the Federal Energy Administration.</p>
</note>
